  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The `toggleShowMore()` method cannot work when _searching for facet values_ as is because it re-renders the widget, and therefore loses the query in the search box.\r\n\r\nHere's what I suggest:\r\n\r\n- If you've started typing in the SFFV searchbox without having toggled \"Show more\", display `limit` results. Otherwise, display `showMoreLimit` results (fixes issue mentioned in @Haroenv's message).\r\n\r\n- If there's no hits returned in the main search, hide the refinement list \"Show more\" button (fixes issue mentioned in @tkrugg's message).\r\n\r\nI've implemented this behavior that you can test [in this story](https://deploy-preview-3082--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories/?selectedKind=RefinementList&selectedStory=with%20search%20and%20show%20more).\r\n\r\nCan you confirm that's what we want to go for so I can unit test it fully?",
    "created_at": "2019-02-25T16:19:24Z",
